Name: Stratification
Description: Condition for using this stage. Use only when multiple top level stages are used.

Name: SamplingUnit
Description: A split results in multiple strata using different sampling plans. For example a study of those who fish which samples those engaged in fishing at particular locations (strata 1) and those who have fishing licenses (strata 2).

Name: TypeOfPlan
Description: Identifies a specific sample frame or frames appropriate for this plan.
